msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/zfs/_index.adoc:2239
msgid ""
"Some of the features provided by ZFS are memory intensive, and may require "
"tuning for maximum efficiency on systems with limited RAM."
